              <span id="reviewTextContainer3173214190" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer134461342251997427">Needed a few days to gather my thoughts on this book. The end result of the the few days brought me clarity. What a wonderful, simplistic narrative of a true friendship. What a beautiful, heartfelt book! One that everyone should read! üò• </span>

          </span>
